155
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:10,583
<i>that Jones felt
spurned by the rejection.</i>

156
00:08:11,526 --> 00:08:13,513
William was
a father figure to him,

157
00:08:13,584 --> 00:08:16,205
a respected mentor.

158
00:08:16,724 --> 00:08:19,636
I would go as far as to say that
all the death and destruction

159
00:08:19,681 --> 00:08:21,479
