Then Bell
needs to come in.

182
00:09:06,195 --> 00:09:07,903
We need to put him
into protective custody.

183
00:09:08,034 --> 00:09:10,194
- Not possible.
- Why not? Where is he?

184
00:09:10,755 --> 00:09:11,911
I can't say.

185
