William Bell for months.

189
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,797
He's been
communicating with me,

190
00:09:21,798 --> 00:09:23,194
strictly electronically.

191
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,326
But what I do know,
though...

192
00:09:26,973 --> 00:09:28,347
is speaking
with William Bell

193
00:09:28,394 --> 00:09:30,850
