a professional matter for you.

194
00:09:31,771 --> 00:09:34,109
In fact,
I'm counting on that.

195
00:09:34,708 --> 00:09:35,829
Stop Jones...

196
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:38,187
And I will personally
arrange a meeting

197
