Should I be concerned?

250
00:15:03,449 --> 00:15:04,367
Should she be?

251
00:15:04,691 --> 00:15:06,468
Peter, hello.

252
00:15:06,695 --> 00:15:07,465
Ms. Sharp.

253
00:15:07,723 --> 00:15:08,910
So what's going on here?

254
